{"id": "art-469", "label": "Art. 469", "title": "Art. 469: Judecarea cererii de redeschidere a procesului", "slug": "art-469", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1806071935\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1409\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1806071935\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 469:\nJudecarea cererii de redeschidere a procesului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_283181117\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1408\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_283181117\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Instan&#355;a,\nascultând concluziile procurorului, ale p&#259;r&#355;ilor &#351;i ale\nsubiec&#355;ilor procesuali principali, examineaz&#259; dac&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1368323050\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1407\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1368323050\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)cererea a fost formulat&#259; în termen &#351;i de\nc&#259;tre o persoan&#259; dintre cele prev&#259;zute la art. 466;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2057357037\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1406\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2057357037\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)au fost invocate temeiuri legale pentru redeschiderea\nprocesului penal;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2067206933\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1405\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2067206933\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)motivele în baza c&#259;rora este formulat&#259; cererea\nnu au fost prezentate într-o cerere anterioar&#259; de redeschidere a\nprocesului penal, care a fost judecat&#259; definitiv.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1813511730\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1404\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1813511730\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Cererea se examineaz&#259; de urgen&#355;&#259;, iar în\ncazul în care persoana condamnat&#259; se afl&#259; în executarea pedepsei cu\nînchisoarea aplicate în cauza a c&#259;rei rejudecare se cere, instan&#355;a\npoate suspenda motivat, în tot sau în parte, executarea hot&#259;rârii &#351;i\npoate dispune respectarea de c&#259;tre condamnat a uneia dintre\nobliga&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 215 alin. (1) &#351;i (2). Dac&#259;\nexecutarea pedepsei cu închisoarea nu a început, instan&#355;a poate dispune\nrespectarea de c&#259;tre condamnat a uneia dintre obliga&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 215 alin. (1) &#351;i (2).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_541158929\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1403\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_541158929\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Dac&#259;\ninstan&#355;a constat&#259; îndeplinirea condi&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute la\nalin. (1), dispune prin încheiere admiterea cererii de redeschidere a\nprocesului penal.</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1103894614\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1402\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1103894614\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>*) Curtea Constitu&#355;ional&#259; admite excep&#355;ia de\nneconstitu&#355;ionalitate &#351;i constat&#259; c&#259; dispozi&#355;iile art.\n469 alin. (3) din Codul de procedur&#259; penal&#259;, în interpretarea\ndat&#259; prin Decizia nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>13 din 3 iulie\n2017</span><span style='color:black'>, pronun&#355;at&#259; de Înalta Curte de\nCasa&#355;ie &#351;i Justi&#355;ie - Completul competent s&#259; judece\nrecursul în interesul legii, în ceea ce prive&#351;te faza procesual&#259; de\nla care se reia procesul penal, sunt neconstitu&#355;ionale.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1137779785\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1401\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1137779785\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dac&#259; instan&#355;a constat&#259; neîndeplinirea\ncondi&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute la art. 466, dispune crin sentin&#355;&#259;\nrespingerea cererii de redeschidere a procesului penal.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_574381601\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1400\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_574381601\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Încheierea prin care este admis&#259; cererea de\nredeschidere a procesului penal poate fi atacat&#259; odat&#259; cu fondul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1961504933\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1399\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1961504933\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Hot&#259;rârea prin care este respins&#259; cererea de\nredeschidere a procesului penal este supus&#259; aceleia&#351;i c&#259;i de\natac ca &#351;i hot&#259;rârea pronun&#355;at&#259; în lipsa persoanei\ncondamnate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_960214265\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1398\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_960214265\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Admiterea cererii de redeschidere a procesului penal\natrage desfiin&#355;area de drept a hot&#259;rârii sau, dup&#259; caz, a\nhot&#259;rârilor pronun&#355;ate în lipsa persoanei condamnate. Judecata se\nreia din faza procesual&#259; desf&#259;&#351;urat&#259; în lipsa persoanei\ncondamnate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1130877805\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1397\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1130877805\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Instan&#355;a redeschide procesul penal prin extindere\n&#351;i cu privire la p&#259;r&#355;ile care nu au formulat cerere, putând\nhot&#259;rî &#351;i în privin&#355;a lor, f&#259;r&#259; s&#259; le poat&#259;\ncrea acestora o situa&#355;ie mai grea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1837406138\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1396\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1837406138\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Odat&#259; cu admiterea cererii de redeschidere a\nprocesului penal, instan&#355;a, din oficiu sau la cererea procurorului, poate\ndispune luarea fa&#355;&#259; de inculpat a uneia dintre m&#259;surile\npreventive prev&#259;zute la art. 202 alin. (4), lit. b)-e). Dispozi&#355;iile\ntitlului V al p&#259;r&#355;ii generale se aplic&#259; în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>"}